{"tid":976214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國買糖要帶身分證","createTime":"2019-01-10T08:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T09:02:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f44e46bdbe025a75c2b154b920ec37cd8e80c1de","tid":976214,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:54:56.000Z","msg":"政治中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n中國政府嚴格管控人民言論自由不是新聞，但近期網路PTT上竟然出現熱烈討論，原因是一則貼文標題寫著「強國買糖都要實名制帶身份證惹」。許多網友百思不得其解，有人去Google查證，才發現原來白糖能做炸彈，讓眾多網友直呼不可思議！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/10/1728759-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F10%2F1728759-XXL.jpg&h=7dc4c0a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發文網友附上一張賣場告示照片，上面用簡體寫著：「溫聲提示，接公安局通知，購買白糖顧客，請攜帶身份證原件」，之後發文者才在外媒報導敘利亞反抗軍，用白糖烹煮再加其他物品，就能自製炸彈的新聞中，懷疑中國官方難道是怕人民會用「土法煉鋼」的方式，自製炸彈嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/27/1707623-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F27%2F1707623-XXL.jpg&h=2e20f7ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息一出，引發網友討論，直言「厲害了我的包子！水可以電解氫跟氧，要不要實名制？」、「鹽也可以做&hellip;那要管制嗎？」、「還有棉花咧 ，咱以後買棉被都得繡名條兒」雖然中國為何買糖，需要出示身分證明文件，還需要官方進一步說明，但網友也大嘆「中國居，自由大不易」的確是不爭的事實！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=483086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D483086&d=5hU%2Bn4bYNeSznHwm6AP4zP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4d001756\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D483086&h=017764d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=483086</a>"},{"pid":"54bce657de32914615bb4f30c1ea0a5abb887db5","tid":976214,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T08:57:05.000Z","msg":"痾屎都要login啦，有幾出奇呀！<br />\nThis is 支那.jpg"},{"pid":"f8fe3dc3539ce3ed0e635b408def80091635fa21","tid":976214,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"真係支爆<br />\n唔好再講咩支那好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}